incident, a city prosecutor says.
   The non-jury trial will take place in Phoenix Municipal Court,
Assistant City Prosecutor Tyler Rich said Thursday.
   The charges of property damage and assault stem from an April 21
run-in between the 7-foot-2-inch, 41-year-old Los Angeles Lakers
center and an Italian tourist at the Metrocenter mall.
